  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK228">
<l>īttuvakku miṉpa maṟiyārko ṟāmuṭaimai</l>
<l>vaittiḻakkum vaṉka ṇavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Do the hard-eyed who lay up and lose their possessions not know the happiness which springs from the pleasure of giving ?</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
